[SHORT DESC]
Mixes Apricorns into Apricorn drinks.
[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Only available in HeartGold and SoulSilver. Apricorn drinks that increase performance at the Pokeathlon are formed after 100 steps when Apricorns are placed in it. Smoothness of the drink increases with time and steps taken.</p>